==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Antecede
<hw>An`te*cede"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>antecedere</ets>; <ets>ante</ets> + <ets>cedere</ets> to go. See
<er>Cede</er>.]</ety> <def>To go before in time or place; to precede; to
surpass.</def> <rj><au>Sir M. Hale.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Antecedence</ent>⟦br⟧
